rows.label: qst201103_0010
rows.name:
The indicated place should
be around here, but...

rows.label: qst201103_0020
rows.name: There's not a single person in sight.

rows.label: qst201103_0030
rows.name: Maybe it was just a prank after all?

rows.label: qst201103_0050
rows.name:
I don't understand why someone would
go to such lengths for a prank.

rows.label: qst201103_0090
rows.name:
Yes, I'm fine. It seems they had
no intention of hitting me.

rows.label: qst201103_0100
rows.name:
...That spear again. What
is the meaning of this?

rows.label: qst201103_0130
rows.name:
Let's chase them... No,
that seems impossible.

rows.label: qst201103_0140
rows.name:
Yes... It would be
impossible to catch up now.

rows.label: qst201103_0150
rows.name:
More importantly, does the spear
have another instruction on it?
